dc_title_s: Clue-map to the principal buildings and thoroughfares of London; Published by John Murray.
dc_description_s: From "Handbook to London as it is", 1868. Shows principal buildings, roads, parks and railroads. 1 map; 26 x 40 cm., folded to 15 x 7 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
